name: Aarav Sharma
bio: A watercolor artist known for painting peaceful Indian landscapes. His work reflects the beauty of rural life and nature.

name: Anvi Gupta
bio: A digital illustrator famous for her bold colors and minimalist character designs. Her modern art style is loved by young audiences.

name: Devansh Verma
bio: An artist who blends Indian folk art with contemporary painting. His creations are inspired by festivals, culture, and traditional stories.

name: Kiara Singh
bio: A portrait and fashion sketch artist recognized for her detailed, stylisg drawings. Her artwork carries a modern and elegant tounch.

name: Manav Tiwari
bio: A street artist specializing in graffiti and wall murals. His vibrant art transforms city spaces into creative visual experiences.

name: Riddhi Agrawal
bio: A mandala and hand-drawn pattern artist whose work reflects balance, calmness, and spiritual harmony.

name: Saanvi Mehra
bio: A contemporary artist blending Indian mythology with modern pop art, known for vibrant, playful canvases.

name: Ishaan Patel
bio: A landscape painter capturing the spirit of Indian monsoons and rural life in lush, detailed scenes.

name: Meera Joshi
bio: A calligraphy and typography artist, fusing Hindi scripts with modern design for unique visual stories.

name: Kabir Deshmukh
bio: A wildlife illustrator, celebrated for his detailed animal portraits and conservation-themed artwork.
